OL,3,CStroud lido could reopen in time for
OL,4,Cthe school summer holidays
OL,6,FStroud's much-loved Stratford Park
OL,7,FLido could reopen this summer as civic
OL,8,Fchiefs have agreed to look at doing
OL,9,Fthe essential repairs needed to make
OL,10,Fit safe as soon as possible.
OL,12,FOpening the outdoor swimming pool for
OL,13,Fthis summer in its current state is
OL,14,Fdeemed to be too dangerous for its
OL,15,Fusers.
OL,17,FHowever, Stroud district councillors
OL,18,Fagreed last night (16 April) a way
OL,19,Fforward which could see the site open
OL,20,Fin time for the school summer holidays.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
