CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776438666
OL,3,CStroud lido could reopen in time for
OL,4,Cthe school summer holidays
OL,6,FThree major hazards were found during
OL,7,Fa risk assessment conducted at the
OL,8,Fsite in February this year.
OL,10,FThese include several cracks in the
OL,11,Fconcrete on the poolside directly
OL,12,Fbeneath and next to the diving board.
OL,13,FAnd the survey found excessive
OL,14,Fcorrosion in the pipework and the pool
OL,15,Ftank.
OL,17,FCouncil chiefs estimate a #5.1million
OL,18,Fupgrade is needed to make the lido
OL,19,Fsustainable for the long term.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
