OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776438666
OL,3,CStroud lido could reopen in time for
OL,4,Cthe school summer holidays
OL,6,FAnd their initial plans would have
OL,7,Finvolved not opening the site for the
OL,8,Fupcoming season.
OL,10,FBut, after mounting public pressure,
OL,11,Fcouncillors have agreed to seek a way
OL,12,Fto reopen Stratford Park Lido this
OL,13,Fsummer, reversing the direction set by
OL,14,Fthe community services and licensing
OL,15,Fcommittee last month.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
