OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776438666
OL,3,CStroud lido could reopen in time for
OL,4,Cthe school summer holidays
OL,6,F"We are acutely conscious of the fact
OL,7,Fthat when the normal lido opening
OL,8,Fseason starts, when the school
OL,9,Fholidays start, and we are throwing
OL,10,Feverything at this, because it is
OL,11,Fabsolutely a priority. But we can't
OL,12,Fopen the pool until it's safe."
OL,14,FThe committee agreed to call on
OL,15,Fofficers to work with qualified
OL,16,Fspecialists to get quotations and a
OL,17,Fcost timetable identifying the minimum
OL,18,Fessential works needed to bring the
OL,19,Flido back into safe use as soon as
OL,20,Fpossible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776438666
OL,3,CStroud lido could reopen in time for
OL,4,Cthe school summer holidays
OL,6,FThey would also look for a costed
OL,7,Ftimetable for a more comprehensive
OL,8,Fplan for the site's refurbishment and
OL,9,Fa schedule of the further works
OL,10,Fidentified that will need to be built
OL,11,Finto a long-term refurbishment and
OL,12,Fmaintenance plan for the lido.
OL,14,FCouncillors agreed that if the costs
OL,15,Fneeded to bring the lido back into use
OL,16,Fas soon as possible are up to #900,000
OL,17,Fin capital costs and #200,000 in
OL,18,Frevenue costs that work starts
OL,19,Fimmediately.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776438666
OL,3,CStroud lido could reopen in time for
OL,4,Cthe school summer holidays
OL,6,FIf the costs are estimated to be
OL,7,Fhigher, a report would be taken to the
OL,8,Fnext council meeting, or an
OL,9,Fextraordinary meeting would be
OL,10,Fconvened, to consider the extent and
OL,11,Fcost of works needed.
OL,13,FThe committee also agreed that they
OL,14,Fwill continue to work with the local
OL,15,Fcommunity and voluntary organisations
OL,16,Fand set up a working group with the
OL,17,Faim of securing a sustainable long-
OL,18,Fterm future of the lido.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
