FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776438666
OL,3,CStroud lido could reopen in time for
OL,4,Cthe school summer holidays
OL,6,FConservative Councillor Lindsey Green
OL,7,Fsaid during the meeting that she had
OL,8,Fconstituents in her ward of Berkeley
OL,9,Fcontact her about the lido.
OL,11,F"The lido does need to be open," she
OL,12,Fsaid. "It fits in with our health and
OL,13,Fwellbeing plan and everything we stand
OL,14,Ffor.J"We need to try and find a way
OL,15,Fforward."
OL,17,FShe said she would like to see more
OL,18,Frobust timeframes around things if
OL,19,Fpossible.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@`O]tD@GOUvD@FOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
