OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776438666
OL,3,CStroud lido could reopen in time for
OL,4,Cthe school summer holidays
OL,6,FThe committee agreed to give
OL,7,Ffortnightly updates on their progress
OL,8,Fto councillors and the community.
OL,10,FAnd Councillor Elizabeth Stanley (L,
OL,11,FCainscross) said with the motion it
OL,12,Ffelt like "the sun's come out from
OL,13,Fbehind the clouds" and that it was
OL,14,F"collaborative working" and a
OL,15,F"positive way forward".
OL,26,@tD@KOUuD@RO]vD@AOUvD@WO]wD@AOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776438666
OL,3,CStroud lido could reopen in time for
OL,4,Cthe school summer holidays
OL,6,FShe also said the council could have
OL,7,Fbeen making these "positive
OL,8,Fsuggestions" in March had better
OL,9,Finformation been presented to the
OL,10,Fcommunity services and licensing
OL,11,Fcommittee.
OL,13,FCouncillor Martin Brown (G, Bisley)
OL,14,Fsaid everybody wants to see the lido
OL,15,Fopen as soon as possible and when it
OL,16,Fis safe to do so.
OL,18,FHe said the amended decision shows a
OL,19,Fway forward and they have a strong
OL,20,Fcommitment to implement it.
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
