PN,43214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776438666
OL,3,CStroud lido could reopen in time for
OL,4,Cthe school summer holidays
OL,6,F"If it is safe to do so, when it is
OL,7,Fsafe to do so, the lido will be open,"
OL,8,Fhe said.
OL,10,F"Let's hope it can be open be by
OL,11,Fschool holidays this summer, if not
OL,12,Fbefore then."
OL,14,FCouncillors voted unanimously to
OL,15,Fapprove the proposals.
OL,17,FCredit: Carmelo Garcia, Local
OL,18,FDemocracy Reporting Service.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@fO]rD@AOUtD@MO]
